tomized quotes to layout planning and\n          white-glove delivery. We make your vision seamless from concept to completion.\n        <\/p>\n      <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\"trade-benefit-card\">\n        <h3 class=\"trade-benefit-title\">Effortless Tax-Free Shopping<\/h3>\n        <div class=\"trade-benefit-divider\"><\/div>\n        <p class=\"trade-benefit-description\">\n          All qualifying trade purchases are automatically tax-exempt at checkout—saving you time and helping you\n          focus on what matters most: the design.\n        <\/p>\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n\n  <style>\nbody {\n            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            color: #333;\n        }\n    .trade-benefits-wrap {\n      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #f5f3ef, #f5f3ef);\n      padding: 60px 20px;\n      position: relative;\n      overflow: hidden;\n      z-index: 0;\n      border-radius: 20px;\n    }\n\n    .trade-benefits-inner {\n      max-width: 1200px;\n      margin: 0 auto;\n      padding: 0 20px;\n      box-sizing: border-box;\n    }\n\n    .trade-benefits-header {\n      text-align: center;\n      margin-bottom: 50px;\n    }\n\n    .trade-benefits-title {\n      font-size: 32px;\n      font-weight: 500;\n      color: #1d1d1d;\n      margin-bottom: 10px;\n    }\n\n    .trade-benefits-header::after {\n      content: '';\n      display: block;\n      width: 60px;\n      height: 2px;\n      background-color: #b28a60;\n      margin: 20px auto 0 auto;\n    }\n\n    .trade-benefits-description {\n      font-size: 18px;\n      color: #666;\n      max-width: 700px;\n      margin: 0 auto;\n      line-height: 1.6;\n    }\n\n    .trade-benefits-list {\n      display: flex;\n      flex-direction: column;\n      gap: 30px;\n      margin-top: 40px;\n    }\n\n    .trade-benefit-card {\n      background-color: #fff;\n      border-radius: 14px;\n      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);\n      padding: 30px 25px;\n      text-align: center;\n      transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n    }\n\n    .trade-benefit-card:hover {\n      transform: translateY(-5px);\n    }\n\n    .trade-benefit-title {\n      font-size: 18px;\n      font-weight: 700;\n      color: #222;\n      margin-bottom: 10px;\n    }\n\n    .trade-benefit-divider {\n      width: 100px;\n      height: 2px;\n      background-color: #b28a60;\n      margin: 0 auto 16px auto;\n    }\n\n    .trade-benefit-description {\n      font-size: 16px;\n      color: #555;\n      line-height: 1.6;\n      margin: 0;\n    }\n@media (max-width: 767px) {\n  .trade-benefits-title {\n    font-size: 26px;\n  }\n\n  .trade-benefits-wrap {\n    padding: 40px 15px;\n  }\n\n  .trade-benefits-inner {\n    padding: 0 10px;\n  }\n\n  .trade-benefits-description {\n    font-size: 16px;\n  }\n\n  .trade-benefit-card {\n    padding: 24px 16px;\n  }\n\n  .trade-benefit-title {\n    font-size: 16px;\n  }\n\n  .trade-benefit-description {\n    font-size: 15px;\n  }\n}\n\n  <\/style>\n<\/section>"}},"richtext_RWVzPb":{"type":"richtext","name":"t:sections.richtext.name","settings":{"overwrite_colors":false,"color":"#000000","background":"#ffffff","narrow_content":false,"horizontal_alignment":"center","pre_title":"TRADE AGREEMENT","title":"<p>Download Our Program Terms<\/p>","heading_size":"h3","content":"<p>Review the full agreement outlining your benefits, eligibility, and terms of the Trade Program.<\/p>","button_label":"View Agreement (PDF)","button_link":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0647\/6231\/4950\/files\/TRADE-PROGRAM.pdf?v=1750695739","button_style":"button--style-2"}},"1748426731f7a15e2c":{"type":"apps","blocks":{"forms_inline_4wNKJj":{"type":"shopify:\/\/apps\/forms\/blocks\/inline\/8744a304-fcb1-4347-b211-bb6b4759a76a","settings":{"form_id":"485257","text_color":"#202020","button_background_color":"#bccf03","button_label_color":"#ffffff","links_color":"#1878b9","e